==制备==
三氯氧化铌是由五氯化铌和氧气化合而成：<ref name=Brauer>{{cite book|entry=Niobium Oxytrichloride|title=Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry|edition=2nd|editor-last=Brauer|editor-first=G.|publisher=Academic Press|date=1963|location=New York|volume=2|page=1307}}</ref>

:NbCl<sub>5</sub>  +  {{sfrac|1|2}} O<sub>2</sub>   →   NbOCl<sub>3</sub>  +  Cl<sub>2</sub>

该反应在约200℃下进行。 NbOCl<sub>3</sub>在[[五氧化二铌|五氧化二铌]]与各种氯化剂如[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]和[[亚硫酰氯|亚硫酰氯]]的反应中也形成了主要的产物。 <ref name=Brauer/><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1007/s11663-997-0125-0 | title = Kinetics of chlorination of niobium pentoxide by carbon tetrachloride | year = 1997 | last1 = Jena | first1 = P. K. | last2 = Brocchi | first2 = E. A. | last3 = Garcia | first3 = R. I. | journal = Metallurgical and Materials Transactions B | volume = 28 | pages = 39–45}}.</ref>
:2 Nb<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>  +  6 CCl<sub>4</sub>   →   4 NbOCl<sub>3</sub>  +  6 COCl<sub>2</sub>
                                          
